nodes.text: 2013 Topps Star Wars Galactic Files Series 2

2013 Topps Star Wars Galactic Files Series 2 is a trading card set released by Topps on August 9, 2013. It is the sequel to Topps' 2012 Topps Star Wars Galactic Files Series 1 and comes with 350 new base cards. The base set features four categories: Characters, Weapons, Planets and Places.

Classic Lines
CL-1. "Will someone get this big walking carpet out of my way?"
CL-2. "What a piece of junk!"
CL-3. "Great shot kid. That was one in a million."
CL-4. "The Force is with you young Skywalker, but you are not a Jedi yet."
CL-5. "You will never find a more wretched hive of scum and villainy."
CL-6. "So this is how liberty dies, with thunderous applause..."
CL-7. "Don't you call me a mindless philosopher, you overweight glob of grease."
CL-8. "General Grievous... You're shorter than I expected."
CL-9. "What if he doesn't survive? He's worth a lot to me."
CL-10. "It's a trap!"
